      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should probably see someone but i cant afford an urgent care visit right now. it's like 2am and i'm just losing it. i have a bottle of extra strength aspirin here too. wouldn't a combo of the two just work better for the inflammation? i feel like if i can just get the pain level down for a few hours i can get through the night. isn't it common to rotate these different types of pain meds?",
